tooltip.avaliproject.aerogel.shift_down: The aerogel is an ephemeral lattice of molecules with incredible structural properties, despite weighing next to nothing.
tooltip.avaliproject.piru_colony.tooltip: Small, barnacle-like colonies which grow long frond-like feeding filaments.
tooltip.avaliproject.nakati_ovoid.toolti: A biolumiscent ovoid. Eventually this will grow into a colony.
tooltip.avaliproject.spicy_jerky.tooltip: Chunks of seasoned jerky, popular with hunters and explorers.
tooltip.avaliproject.kiri_fruit.tooltip: The fruiting body of a subterranean slime mould. This one has already sporing though.
tooltip.avaliproject.kiri_cider.tooltip: Slightly fermented kiri juice including a bit the ground-up rind and a dash of nakati
tooltip.avaliproject.tucker.tooltip: Just like normal cookies, only spikier.
tooltip.avaliproject.woven_graphene.tool: Grapene that's been woven specially for use in avaly crafting stations.
tooltip.avaliproject.woven_fabric.toolti: A small square of woven fabric
tooltip.avaliproject.protosteel_ingot.to: A complex nanite-infused alloy, used to create strong weapons and armour.
tooltip.avaliproject.nanite_injector.too: A small Nanite Injector, used in crafting recipes.
tooltip.avaliproject.nakati_bark.tooltip: The spicy bark of the nakati plant. Usually ground up before use.
tooltip.avaliproject.avali_bottle.toolti: A bottle made in aerogel, able to contain and conserve it's content
tooltip.avaliproject.aeromer.tooltip: All the benefits of aerogel, but with structural integrity!
tooltip.avaliproject.titanium_ingot.tool: Result of the smelting of titanium ore primarily found in temperate climate.
tooltip.avaliproject.durasteel_ingot.too: Result of the smelting of durasteel ore primarily found in arid climate.
tooltip.avaliproject.refined_aegisalt.to: Result of the smelting of aegisalt ore primarily found in cold climate.
tooltip.avaliproject.piru_noodle.tooltip: Sweet noodles made from piru frond flour, a staple for young avali.
tooltip.avaliproject.piru_flour.tooltip: Piru frond, ground down into a versatile flour-like substance. Not exactly edible.
tooltip.avaliproject.kiri_curry.tooltip: Spicy meat noodles with a rich kiri sauce.
tooltip.avaliproject.groou.tooltip: Juicy and sweet, similar to jelly.
tooltip.avaliproject.avalon_taco.tooltip: Super-hot nakati-spiced taco; sometimes eaten on a dare by non-avali.
tooltip.avaliproject.avali_muffin.toolti: It was covered with kiri jam and decorated with some dried fruit of Tucker
tooltip.avaliproject.kirikiri_pie.toolti: A sour oculemon-filled pie with a sweet meringue topping.
tooltip.avaliproject.piru_frond.tooltip: A long, fibrous frond from a piru barnacle.
tooltip.avaliproject.avali_hoe.tooltip: An Avali version of the classic hoe.
tooltip.avaliproject.avali_axe.tooltip: An Avali version of the classic axe.
tooltip.avaliproject.avali_pickaxe.toolt: An Avali version of the classic pickaxe.
tooltip.avaliproject.avali_sword.tooltip: An Avali version of the classic sword.
tooltip.avaliproject.piru_frond.tooltip: A long, fibrous frond from a piru barnacle.
